name: dwt_346
description:
Unfolding of a dwt_346 sparse matrix into a lattice. The original matrix describes a structural problem first documented by G. Everstine and D. Taylor in 1980. In this simulation, the matrix is represented as a lattice with 346 nodes which undergoes a process of unfolding until it reaches equilibrium. 

@lukapiskorec, mp4, 1000 x 1000 pix, 300 frames
